│   │   │   └── test_table_2d_manager.py
│   │   └── test_job_stage_processing_time_manager.py
│   └── util/
│       └── test_text_data_parser.py
```

## 🧪 Testing

To run the tests, use the following command:

```sh
pytest tests/
```

## Installation

```sh
pip install schore
```

